<CD-RAT><Entry><HWD>02\3\1\Past Simple and Continuous</HWD><Activity><GapFillDropdown><Title>Past Simple and Continuous</Title><Instruction>Click on the correct words.</Instruction><ContentGapFillDropdown><PersonName><font face="Verdana" size="12" color="#000000">1<TAB></TAB></font></PersonName>He<Dropdown><Choice is-correct="1">broke</Choice><Choice>was breaking</Choice></Dropdown>his leg while he <Dropdown><Choice>skied</Choice><Choice is-correct="1">was skiing</Choice></Dropdown>.<br></br><PersonName><font face="Verdana" size="12" color="#000000">2<TAB></TAB></font></PersonName><Dropdown><Choice>Were you knowing</Choice><Choice is-correct="1">Did you know</Choice></Dropdown>about the meeting?<br></br><PersonName><font face="Verdana" size="12" color="#000000">3<TAB></TAB></font></PersonName>I<Dropdown><Choice is-correct="1">was</Choice><Choice>was being</Choice></Dropdown>nervous because I thought someone<Dropdown><Choice>followed</Choice><Choice is-correct="1">was following</Choice></Dropdown>me.<br></br><PersonName><font face="Verdana" size="12" color="#000000">4<TAB></TAB></font></PersonName>She<Dropdown><Choice>listened</Choice><Choice is-correct="1">was listening</Choice></Dropdown>to a CD when suddenly the lights <Dropdown><Choice>were going</Choice><Choice is-correct="1">went</Choice></Dropdown>off.<br></br><PersonName><font face="Verdana" size="12" color="#000000">5<TAB></TAB></font></PersonName>How many times <Dropdown><Choice is-correct="1">did you see</Choice><Choice>were you seeing</Choice></Dropdown>that film when it was on in London?<br></br><PersonName><font face="Verdana" size="12" color="#000000">6<TAB></TAB></font></PersonName>Sorry, I didn't answer because when you <Dropdown><Choice is-correct="1">called</Choice><Choice>were calling</Choice></Dropdown>, I<Dropdown><Choice>had</Choice><Choice is-correct="1">was having</Choice></Dropdown>a shower.<br></br><PersonName><font face="Verdana" size="12" color="#000000">7<TAB></TAB></font></PersonName>Ten cars <Dropdown><Choice>crossed</Choice><Choice is-correct="1">were crossing</Choice></Dropdown>when the bridge <Dropdown><Choice>was falling</Choice><Choice is-correct="1">fell</Choice></Dropdown>into the river.<br></br><PersonName><font face="Verdana" size="12" color="#000000">8<TAB></TAB></font></PersonName>I'm sure it <Dropdown><Choice>was being</Choice><Choice is-correct="1">was</Choice></Dropdown>your wife that I saw. <br></br><PersonName><font face="Verdana" size="12" color="#ffffff">8<TAB></TAB></font></PersonName><Dropdown><Choice>Did she wear</Choice><Choice is-correct="1">Was she wearing</Choice></Dropdown>a black dress?<br></br><PersonName><font face="Verdana" size="12" color="#000000">9<TAB></TAB></font></PersonName>Who<Dropdown><Choice>did you talk</Choice><Choice is-correct="1">were you talking</Choice></Dropdown>to this morning? <br></br><PersonName><font face="Verdana" size="12" color="#ffffff">9<TAB></TAB></font></PersonName>I<Dropdown><Choice is-correct="1">recognised</Choice><Choice>was recognising</Choice></Dropdown>her face.<br></br><PersonName><font face="Verdana" size="12" color="#000000">10<TAB></TAB></font></PersonName>Jack <Dropdown><Choice is-correct="1">didn't see</Choice><Choice>wasn't seeing</Choice></Dropdown>me this morning, because he<Dropdown><Choice is-correct="1">was cycling</Choice><Choice>cycled</Choice></Dropdown>the other way. </ContentGapFillDropdown></GapFillDropdown></Activity></Entry></CD-RAT>